### Create Case
POST http://localhost:8086/collections/cases
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "loanId": "loan-001",
  "userId": "user-123",
  "bucket": "D1",
  "principalDue": 520,
  "currency": "GHS"
}

### Record Action
POST http://localhost:8086/collections/cases/{{caseId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "actionType": "CALL",
      "actor": "collector-1",
      "note": "Promised to pay tomorrow"
}

### Loan Event -> Auto Case
POST http://localhost:8086/events/loan
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "eventType": "OVERDUE_BUCKET_CHANGED",
  "loanId": "loan-002",
  "userId": "user-789",
  "bucket": "D3",
  "principalDue": "800.00",
  "currency": "GHS"
}

### Payment Event -> Auto Close
POST http://localhost:8086/events/payment
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "eventType": "REPAYMENT_POSTED",
  "loanId": "loan-001",
  "remainingDue": "0",
  "actor": "payment-svc"
}
